---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Consulting"
  description="AHoosh consulting services — AI strategy, market research, business model, operations, data, website, content, automation, and Persian market support."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background:linear-gradient(160deg,#03142E 0%,#010A18 100%);padding:48px 24px 40px;text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.1);">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Consulting</div>
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(22px,6vw,36px);letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:10px;">Consulting Services</h1>
    <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--silver-dim);line-height:1.7;max-width:520px;margin:0 auto;">
      AHoosh helps companies, startups, and decision-makers use AI, research, and data
      to understand problems, evaluate options, and build practical solutions.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section style="padding:40px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.08);max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="section-eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:20px;">Nine Service Areas</div>

    <!-- 01 -->
    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-left:3px solid var(--gold);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:16px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;">01 · AI Strategy &amp; Adoption</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:8px;">Understand where AI actually helps</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--silver-dim);">Helping companies understand where AI can actually help, what tools to use, and what to avoid. No hype — just a practical map of what applies to your situation and what the realistic outcomes are.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 02 -->
    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-left:3px solid var(--gold);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:16px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;">02 · Market Research &amp; Opportunity Analysis</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:8px;">Research before you commit</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--silver-dim);">Researching markets, competitors, customers, pricing, demand, and entry opportunities. Turning public data and AI-assisted research into clear answers about whether an opportunity is real and how to approach it.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 03 -->
    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-left:3px solid var(--gold);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:16px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;">03 · Business Model &amp; Strategy</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:8px;">Clarity on positioning and direction</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--silver-dim);">Helping founders and companies clarify positioning, revenue models, offers, and growth paths. Useful when you are starting something new, pivoting, or trying to figure out why growth has stalled.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 04 -->
    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-left:3px solid var(--gold);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:16px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;">04 · Operations Improvement</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:8px;">Fix what slows you down</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--silver-dim);">Finding manual, repetitive, or unclear workflows and redesigning them with better tools and processes. The goal is always to free up time and reduce errors — not to add complexity.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 05 -->
    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-left:3px solid var(--gold);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:16px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;">05 · Data &amp; Decision Support</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:8px;">Turn data into decisions</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--silver-dim);">Building dashboards, reports, data structures, and decision-support models from available information. Helps teams stop guessing and start making decisions from real signals.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 06 -->
    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-left:3px solid var(--gold);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:16px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;">06 · Digital Presence &amp; Website Strategy</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:8px;">A website that works for you</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--silver-dim);">Improving websites, content structure, user flows, credibility, and conversion logic. Design, build, and run on modern stacks — built to perform and maintainable without constant developer dependency.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 07 -->
    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-left:3px solid var(--gold);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:16px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;">07 · Content &amp; Thought Leadership</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:8px;">Build authority with real content</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--silver-dim);">Creating research-based articles, explainers, reports, and educational content. Not generic blog posts — actual analysis that positions you or your company as a credible source in your field.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 08 -->
    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-left:3px solid var(--gold);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:16px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;">08 · Automation &amp; Tooling</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:8px;">Practical automation, not vendor lock-in</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--silver-dim);">Designing practical automations using AI tools, no-code/low-code systems, APIs, and existing software. Built to solve specific problems without adding fragile systems that break when someone leaves.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 09 -->
    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-left:3px solid var(--gold);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;">09 · Persian Market &amp; Language Support</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:8px;">Bridge the language and culture gap</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--silver-dim);">Supporting Persian-language users, content, research, localization, and business communication. Useful for companies entering Persian-speaking markets or building products for Persian users globally.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section style="padding:40px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.08);max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="section-eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:16px;">How It Works</div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;margin-bottom:24px;align-items:flex-start;">
      <div style="flex-shrink:0;width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(215,161,61,0.1);border:1.5px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.35);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:var(--gold);">1</div>
      <div><div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:4px;">First Conversation</div><div style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);">We talk about what you are trying to solve. No forms, no templates — just a direct conversation to understand the situation.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;margin-bottom:24px;align-items:flex-start;">
      <div style="flex-shrink:0;width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(215,161,61,0.1);border:1.5px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.35);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:var(--gold);">2</div>
      <div><div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:4px;">Diagnosis</div><div style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);">I map what is actually happening — using research, data, and direct observation — and identify where the right intervention will have the most impact.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;margin-bottom:24px;align-items:flex-start;">
      <div style="flex-shrink:0;width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(215,161,61,0.1);border:1.5px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.35);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:var(--gold);">3</div>
      <div><div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:4px;">Build &amp; Deliver</div><div style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);">We produce the output together — a research report, a strategy document, a working tool, or a live system. Scope is defined before work starts.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;">
      <div style="flex-shrink:0;width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(215,161,61,0.1);border:1.5px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.35);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:var(--gold);">4</div>
      <div><div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:4px;">Handoff or Ongoing</div><div style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);">You get everything documented so your team can continue independently — or we stay involved for ongoing support. Your choice.</div></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA band -->
  <section style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(215,161,61,0.08) 0%,rgba(3,20,46,0.6) 100%);border-top:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.15);padding:40px 24px;text-align:center;">
    <div style="max-width:480px;margin:0 auto;">
      <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:20px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.3;">Contact AHoosh to discuss the right scope</h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--silver-dim);margin-bottom:24px;">Tell me what you are trying to understand, build, improve, or decide.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="display:inline-block;min-width:200px;">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
